(1, 'custom-software-development', '{\"hero\":{\"title\":\"Custom Software Development\",\"backgroundImage\":\"3.webp\",\"mobileBackgroundImage\":\"m3.webp\",\"breadcrumbs\":[{\"label\":\"Home\",\"href\":\"/\"},{\"label\":\"Services\",\"href\":\"/services\"}],\"subtitle\":\"Empowering Businesses with Intelligent AI Solutions for Automation and Insights\"},\"introduction\":\"At AllSpark Technologies (AST), we don’t believe in one-size-fits-all solutions. As a trusted bespoke software development firm, we craft solutions tailored to your business, ensuring agility, scalability, and long-term growth. From concept to deployment, we deliver high-performance applications that integrate seamlessly with your workflows, driving tangible outcomes.\",\"services\":{\"title\":\"At AllSpark Technologies (AST), we don’t believe in one-size-fits-all solutions. As a trusted bespoke software development firm, we craft solutions tailored to your business, ensuring agility, scalability, and long-term growth. From concept to deployment, we deliver high-performance applications that integrate seamlessly with your workflows, driving tangible outcomes.\",\"cards\":[{\"title\":\"Enterprise Software Development\",\"content\":\"Large organizations demand scalable, secure, and adaptable systems. As a premier enterprise software development company, AST creates custom-built software that automates operations and strengthens infrastructure for lasting innovation and growth.\"},{\"title\":\"Bespoke Software Development\",\"content\":\"Off-the-shelf solutions don’t always align with your needs. As a bespoke software development provider, AST delivers customized software that fits your workflows, enhances performance, and eliminates inefficiencies.\"},{\"title\":\"Product Development & Digital Transformation\",\"content\":\"AST builds full-featured, market-ready products—from SaaS platforms to tools for customer engagement. We drive digital transformation by developing user-friendly software that solves real-world challenges.\"},{\"title\":\"Seamless System Integration\",\"content\":\"Disconnected systems hinder efficiency. Our dev software services include secure system integrations and API-driven automation, helping applications exchange data efficiently and comply with modern security standards.\"},{\"title\":\"Custom API Development\",\"content\":\"We design scalable, secure APIs using REST and GraphQL for efficient system communication. Our APIs improve backend performance while boosting software usability and reliability.\"},{\"title\":\"Future-Ready Technology Solutions\",\"content\":\"Future-proofing your business is essential. AST uses the latest tools and practices to build enterprise-grade software that aligns with your evolving needs, supports compliance, and facilitates agile business operations.\"}]},\"approach\":{\"title\":\"Our Approach to Custom Software Development\",\"cards\":[{\"iconColor\":\"blue\",\"title\":\"Clear & Collaborative Process\",\"content\":\"Collaboration fuels our success. AST involves clients at every stage—from discovery to post-launch—ensuring transparency and alignment. Our Agile methodology enables seamless communication and continuous progress tracking.\"},{\"iconColor\":\"blue\",\"title\":\"Human-Centered Design\",\"content\":\"User satisfaction drives software success. Our team implements human-centered design and usability testing to create intuitive solutions that maximize engagement and productivity.\"},{\"iconColor\":\"blue\",\"title\":\"Continuous Optimization & Agile Development\",\"content\":\"With agile software development, we refine software continuously through iterative improvements and performance-driven updates. This ensures flexibility and feature-rich solutions that scale with your business.\"},{\"iconColor\":\"blue\",\"title\":\"Security & Compliance as a Priority\",\"content\":\"As a software development agency in NYC, we prioritize security and data protection. Our custom applications are built with enterprise-grade protection, compliant with HIPAA, GDPR, and ISO 27001 standards.\"}]},\"whyChoose\":{\"title\":\"Why Choose AST for Custom Software Development?\",\"stats\":[{\"id\":1,\"label\":\"10+ Years of Excellence in delivering cutting-edge solutions\",\"value\":10,\"suffix\":\"+\"},{\"id\":2,\"label\":\"150+ Software Development Projects Delivered\",\"value\":150,\"suffix\":\"+\"},{\"id\":3,\"label\":\"50+ Technologies Used in Real-World Projects\",\"value\":50,\"suffix\":\"+\"},{\"id\":4,\"label\":\"300+ Specialists including expert Node.js developers, UI/UX engineers, and system architects\",\"value\":300,\"suffix\":\"+\"}]},\"faqs\":{\"title\":\"FAQs: Your Questions Answered\",\"items\":[{\"question\":\"Why should I opt for custom software instead of ready-made solutions?\",\"answer\":\"Custom software aligns precisely with your workflows, offering better performance, flexibility, and cost-efficiency over time. AST’s custom development ensures unique features tailored to your business—ideal for industries like finance, retail, healthcare, and more.\"},{\"question\":\"How long does custom software development take?\",\"answer\":\"Project timelines vary. A small MVP might take 3–4 months, while enterprise-grade software for retail shops or SaaS platforms may require 6–12 months. AST provides a clear roadmap at the start of every project.\"},{\"question\":\"What determines the cost of custom software development?\",\"answer\":\"Pricing depends on the tech stack, feature set, integrations, and overall scope. AST provides detailed quotes and transparent breakdowns to match your needs and budget.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I modify my software later?\",\"answer\":\"Absolutely. Our solutions are built for evolution. Whether scaling a product or integrating third-party APIs, we ensure flexibility and future-ready architecture.\"},{\"question\":\"Will I have control over the development process?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. With AST, you’ll work alongside your dedicated software developer in NYC and participate in every sprint. Our client-first approach ensures complete visibility from design to delivery.\"},{\"question\":\"Do you have software development case studies?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, we’ve worked on a variety of industries and platforms. Contact us to request specific software development case studies related to your domain or technology preference.\"}]},\"script\":{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"name\":\"Custom Software Development | Bespoke Dev Services NYC\",\"url\":\"https://allsparktechnologies.com/services/custom-software-development\",\"description\":\"Custom software solutions tailored to your business. Trusted bespoke development company in NYC delivering scalable, high-performance applications.\",\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"AllSpark Technologies\",\"url\":\"https://allsparktechnologies.com\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://allsparktechnologies.com/logo.png\"},\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"streetAddress\":\"638 Knollwood Road\",\"addressLocality\":\"Franklin Lakes\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"postalCode\":\"07417\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}}]},\"metadata\":{\"title\":\"Custom Software Development | Bespoke Dev Services NYC\",\"description\":\"Explore custom software solutions tailored to your business. Bespoke development in NYC.\",\"metadataBase\":\"https://allsparktechnologies.com/\",\"alternates\":{\"canonical\":\"services/custom-software-development\"},\"openGraph\":{\"title\":\"Custom Software Development | Bespoke Dev Services NYC\",\"description\":\"Explore custom software solutions tailored to your business. Bespoke development in NYC.\",\"url\":\"https://allsparktechnologies.com/services/custom-software-development\",\"type\":\"website\",\"siteName\":\"AllSpark Technologies\",\"images\":[{\"url\":\"https://allsparktechnologies.com/assets/images/custom-software-og.jpg\",\"width\":1200,\"height\":630,\"alt\":\"Custom Software Development\"}]},\"robots\":{\"index\":true,\"follow\":true},\"twitter\":{\"card\":\"summary_large_image\",\"title\":\"Custom Software Development | Bespoke Dev Services NYC\",\"description\":\"Explore custom software solutions tailored to your business. Bespoke development in NYC.\",\"images\":[\"https://allsparktechnologies.com/assets/images/custom-software-og.jpg\"]}}}'),
(2, 'web-and-app-development', '{\"hero\":{\"title\":\"Web & App Development\",\"backgroundImage\":\"10.webp\",\"mobileBackgroundImage\":\"m10.webp\",\"breadcrumbs\":[{\"label\":\"Home\",\"href\":\"/\"},{\"label\":\"Services\",\"href\":\"/services\"}],\"subtitle\":\"Architecting High-Performance, Scalable, and User-Centric Applications\"},\"introduction\":\"At All Spark Technologies (AST), we don’t just build digital products—we architect high-performance, scalable, and user-centric web and mobile apps that drive real business results. As a leading web app development company, our goal is to help businesses—from startups to enterprises—turn their ideas into reliable, functional, and engaging applications.\\nWhether you’re seeking to build a progressive web app (PWA), an e-commerce solution, or a robust SaaS platform, we use the latest technology for website development to ensure your solution is secure, fast, and future-ready. AST combines technical excellence with creative UX to deliver digital experiences that engage users and scale with your growth.\",\"services\":{\"title\":\"At All Spark Technologies (AST), we don’t just build digital products—we architect high-performance, scalable, and user-centric web and mobile apps that drive real business results. As a leading web app development company, our goal is to help businesses—from startups to enterprises—turn their ideas into reliable, functional, and engaging applications.\\nWhether you’re seeking to build a progressive web app (PWA), an e-commerce solution, or a robust SaaS platform, we use the latest technology for website development to ensure your solution is secure, fast, and future-ready. AST combines technical excellence with creative UX to deliver digital experiences that engage users and scale with your growth.\",\"cards\":[{\"title\":\"Tailored Web Application Development\",\"content\":\"Unlike cookie-cutter platforms, our custom-built applications are designed to meet specific industry challenges. Fr