e site development, or fully custom ecommerce software development company solutions.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-3\",\n          \"ques\": \"How long does it take to build an ecommerce store?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Timelines depend on project complexity. A simple ecommerce web site development can take 6–8 weeks, while large B2B ecommerce development services or ecommerce marketplace development projects may take several months. As an ecommerce web development firm, we provide clear timelines before starting.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-4\",\n          \"ques\": \"Can you upgrade or optimize my existing ecommerce site?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Yes. Our ecommerce web development agency offers redesigns, migrations, and optimization. Whether you need Magento ecommerce site development, Shopify ecommerce development services, or enterprise ecommerce software development services, we can rebuild and scale your platform.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-5\",\n          \"ques\": \"Do you build ecommerce mobile apps?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Yes. As an ecommerce mobile app development company, our ecommerce app developers build custom iOS and Android solutions. This ensures your customers enjoy seamless shopping experiences across devices.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  }'),
(8, 'full-stack-development ', 'web-and-app-development', '{\n    \"title\": \"Full Stack Web Development Services\",\n    \"section2\": {\n      \"title\": \"Build Reliable Digital Solutions With Confidence\",\n      \"des\": \"Choosing to hire full stack developers can feel overwhelming. Many businesses worry about hiring the wrong talent, wasting money on freelancers, or ending up with code that doesn’t scale. At Allspark Technologies, we remove those worries. Our dedicated full stack developers deliver complete web development solutions covering both front end and back end web development, so your website or application runs smoothly, securely, and grows with your business. Whether you need a freelance full stack developer for a short project or a long-term full stack developer hire, we ensure reliable delivery every time.\"\n    },\n    \"section3\": {\n      \"title\": \"Full Stack Web Development Services We Offer\",\n      \"image\": \"img1.png\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Development Without Gaps\",\n          \"description\": \"A common concern is that separate teams for front end and back end web development may create miscommunication and errors. With Allspark, you hire full stack developers who handle everything end to end. Our services include front end web development services, back end web development, API integration, database design, and full stack web development services for scalable applications.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Clear Hiring Options Without Surprises\",\n          \"description\": \"Many worry about unclear costs or the risks of freelance full stack developers. At Allspark, you can choose flexible models, hire full stack developers full-time, part-time, or remote based on your project needs. As a transparent partner, we ensure predictable pricing with no hidden fees.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Visibility That Attracts Users\",\n          \"description\": \"One maj