ning your goals, challenges, and audience. As a trusted full stack development company, we create a roadmap that combines the best front end and back end web development solutions.\",\n          \"margin\": \"0px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 2,\n          \"title\": \"Custom Design & Development\",\n          \"description\": \"Our full stack developers build user-friendly designs and robust applications. From front end UI to back end logic, we deliver fast, secure, and scalable platforms.\",\n          \"margin\": \"100px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 3,\n          \"title\": \"Integration & Optimization\",\n          \"description\": \"We connect your system with third-party tools, APIs, and databases while ensuring SEO optimization for visibility.\",\n          \"margin\": \"200px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 4,\n          \"title\": \"Testing & Ongoing Support\",\n          \"description\": \"Every full stack developer on our team ensures stability through rigorous testing. Post-launch, we provide continuous support and updates to keep your system performing at its best.\",\n          \"margin\": \"300px\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section6\": {\n      \"image\": \"img2.png\",\n      \"title\": \"Build Digital Success That Lasts\",\n      \"des\": \"A website or app is more than just code, it’s the backbone of your digital presence. At All Spark Technologies, we provide front end and back end web development that drives performance, scalability, and long-term growth. Our full stack developers combine technical expertise with business-focused solutions to deliver applications that work seamlessly across devices and platforms.\",\n      \"des2\": \"From enterprise-level full stack web development services to freelance full stack developer support, we cover every model your business needs. Whether you are hiring a full stack developer remote, looking for custom integrations, or need ongoing support, Allspark is your trusted partner.\"\n    },\n    \"section7\": {\n      \"quote\": \"Allspark’s full stack developers built our application faster than expected. It’s stable, user-friendly, and ready to scale.\",\n      \"author\": \"Mark T., SaaS Founder\"\n    },\n    \"section8\": {\n      \"image\": \"img3.png\",\n      \"title\": \"Why Choose Us\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Proven Full Stack Expertise\",\n          \"description\": \"Years of experience delivering complete front end and back end web development projects across industries.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Performance and Scalability\",\n          \"description\": \"Applications designed to handle growth, speed, and secure integrations.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Security and Compliance\",\n          \"description\": \"We follow strict security standards to keep your data and applications safe.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Ongoing Support & Maintenance\",\n          \"description\": \"From updates to troubleshooting, our team ensures your application always runs smoothly.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section9\": {\n      \"title\": \"Industries We Serve\",\n      \"para\": \"We provide full stack solutions across industries such as:\",\n      \"industries\": [\n        \"SaaS & Technology Platforms\",\n        \"E-commerce & Online Stores\",\n        \"Healthcare & Pharma Solutions\",\n        \"Finance & Fintech Applications\",\n        \"Education & E-Learning Platforms\",\n        \"Manufacturing & Enterprise Systems\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"faq\": {\n      \"title\": \"Frequently Asked Questions\",\n      \"faqs\": [\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-1\",\n          \"ques\": \"Why should I hire a full stack developer instead of separate front end and back end developers?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Hiring a full stack developer saves time and cost because one expert manages both front end and back end web development, ensuring smooth coordination and faster delivery.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-2\",\n          \"ques\": \"How much does it cost to hire full stack developers?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Costs depend on project size, features, and engagement model. We offer flexible hiring, freelance full stack developer, dedicated full-time, or remote developer options.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-3\",\n          \"ques\": \"Can I hire a full stack developer remote for my project?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Yes. Our remote full stack developers provide the same quality and support as in-house teams, ensuring efficient collaboration across time zones.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-4\",\n          \"ques\": \"What’s the difference between a front end web developer vs back end web developer?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Front end web developers focus on user interfaces, while back end developers manage databases, servers, and application logic. A full stack developer does both.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-5\",\n          \"ques\": \"Can you upgrade or optimize my existing application?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Yes. Our team can redesign, optimize, or scale your existing platform with modern full stack web development services.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-6\",\n          \"ques\": \"Why choose Allspark over freelance developers?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Unlike freelancers, we provide a team of vetted, dedicated full stack developers with post-launch support, ensuring your project is stable and future ready.\"\n        }\n        \n      ]\n    }\n  }'),
(9, 'web-portal-development', 'web-and-app-development', '{\n    \"title\": \"Web Portal Development Services\",\n    \"section2\": {\n      \"title\": \"Build Digital Gateways That Work\",\n      \"des\": \"Choosing a web portal development company can feel overwhelming. Many business portals that are slow, confusing, or fail to attract users. At Allspark Technologies, we deliver web portal development services designed to remove those concerns. Our web portals developers build secure, scalable, and user-friendly platforms that connect people, data, and processes. Whether you need B2B web portal development, customer self-service portals, or enterprise solutions, we create digital gateways that bring measurable results.\"\n    },\n    \"section3\": {\n      \"title\": \"Web Portal Development Services We Offer\",\n      \"image\": \"img1.png\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Development Without Complexity\",\n          \"description\": \"Many worry about how to develop a web portal that truly meets business needs. As a trusted web portal development company, we provide custom web portal development, B2B web portals development, employee intranet solutions, and customer portals. Just like the Home Depot web portal development team built systems for scale, we engineer portals that simplify processes and drive engagement.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Clear Pricing Without Surprises\",\n          \"description\": \"One common concern is hidden costs. At Allspark, our web portal development services are structured around clear, flexible packages. Whether you start with a simple business portal or an enterprise-level platform, we provide transparent pricing that grows with your needs.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Engagement That Drives Value\",\n          \"description\": \"A portal is useless if no one uses it. That’s why our custom web portal development process includes user-friendly design, advanced searc