r web portals development process, we also optimize for speed, SEO, and mobile responsiveness.\",\n          \"margin\": \"200px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 4,\n          \"title\": \"Testing & Continuous Support\",\n          \"description\": \"Every custom web portal development project undergoes rigorous testing. Post-launch, we provide ongoing updates, support, and performance monitoring to keep your portal reliable.\",\n          \"margin\": \"300px\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section6\": {\n      \"image\": \"img2.png\",\n      \"title\": \"Build Portals That Empower Growth\",\n      \"des\": \"A web portal is more than a platform, it’s your business’s digital gateway. As a trusted web portal development company in the USA, Allspark Technologies delivers scalable, secure, and user-focused solutions. From B2B web portal development to employee intranets and customer platforms, we ensure every project is built to perform.\",\n      \"des2\": \"Our expertise covers custom web portal development, integrations, and performance optimization. With Allspark, you don’t just get a portal, you get a long-term partner that helps your business grow through technology. Businesses often wonder if a web portal development company can guarantee protection of sensitive data while still allowing smooth connections with CRMs, ERPs, or third-party tools. Our web portals developers build solutions that are secure by default, optimized for performance, and designed to grow with your business.\"\n    },\n    \"section7\": {\n      \"quote\": \"Allspark built our customer portal on time and beyond expectations. It’s fast, secure, and adoption across our teams was seamless.\",\n      \"author\": \"Mark L., B2B Client\"\n    },\n    \"section8\": {\n      \"image\": \"img3.png\",\n      \"title\": \"Why Choose Us\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Proven Portal Expertise\",\n          \"description\": \"We bring years of experience in cus