ze in building B2B platforms that streamline communication, transactions, and data sharing.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-4\",\n          \"ques\": \"How long does it take to develop a portal?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Timelines vary by scope. A simple portal may take 6–8 weeks, while enterprise web portals development projects can take several months.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-5\",\n          \"ques\": \"Can you upgrade or optimize an existing portal?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Absolutely. We provide migration, redesign, and optimization services for outdated systems.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-6\",\n          \"ques\": \"Why choose Allspark over others?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Allspark combines technical expertise, clear pricing, and long-term support, making us a reliable web portal development partner.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n}'),
(10, 'cms-development', 'web-and-app-development', '{\n    \"title\": \"CMS Development Services\",\n    \"section2\": {\n      \"title\": \"Custom CMS for Simplified Content Workflows\",\n      \"des\": \"Choosing the right CMS development company can feel overwhelming. Many businesses worry about hidden costs, complex systems, or being locked into a platform they can’t manage. At Allspark Technologies, we make CMS development simple, transparent, and tailored to your needs. Our CMS web development services help you launch, manage, and scale your digital presence without technical headaches. Whether you need WordPress CMS development services, custom CMS development for enterprise projects, or headless CMS development for modern apps, our expert CMS developers build solutions that balance power with ease of use.\"\n    },\n    \"section3\": {\n      \"title\": \"Full CMS Development Services We Provide\",\n      \"image\": \"img1.png\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Custom CMS Development\",\n          \"description\": \"Our custom CMS development company creates tailored platforms that fit your workflows, security needs, and growth goals.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"WordPress CMS Development\",\n          \"description\": \"As a WordPress CMS development company, we deliver fast, SEO-friendly, and user-friendly websites with easy content management.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Drupal & Craft CMS Development\",\n          \"description\": \"From Drupal CMS development company solutions to Craft CMS developers for creative websites, we build powerful, flexible systems.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Headless CMS Development\",\n          \"description\": \"With our headless CMS development services (like Sanity, Sitefinity, and HubSpot CMS development), we future-proof your digital platforms.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Enterprise CMS Solutions\",\n          \"description\": \"We specialize in Sitecore CMS development, Umbraco CMS developer solutions, and advanced integrations for large organizations.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section4\": {\n      \"title\": \"Seamless CMS Integration for Businesses\",\n      \"des\": \"A CMS should not just manage content, it should empower your business. As a leading CMS development company, Allspark delivers scalable CMS web development services that integrate smoothly with your existing workflows. From WordPress CMS development services to headless CMS development, our solutions help businesses publish, manage, and optimize content effortlessly.\"\n    },\n    \"section5\": {\n      \"title\": \"How We Work With You\",\n      \"steps\": [\n        {\n          \"step\": 1,\n          \"title\": \"Discovery & Planning\",\n          \"description\": \"We understand your goals, challenges, and platform preferences before suggesting the right CMS web development services.\",\n          \"margin\": \"0px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 2,\n          \"title\": \"Custom Development\",\n          \"description\": \"Our CMS web developers build or customize platforms to match your exact business needs.\",\n          \"margin\": \"100px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 3,\n          \"title\": \"Testing & Launch\",\n          \"description\": \"We ensure your CMS is secure, fast, and user-friendly before going live.\",\n          \"margin\": \"200px\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"step\": 4,\n          \"title\": \"Ongoing Support\",\n          \"description\": \"From updates to training, our CMS website development services keep your system running smoothly.\",\n          \"margin\": \"300px\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section6\": {\n      \"image\": \"img2.png\",\n      \"title\": \"Client Success with Custom CMS Solutions\",\n      \"des\": \"Your CMS is more than a content tool, it’s the backbone of your online presence. Many businesses fear their system will become outdated or too rigid. That’s why Allspark focuses on long-term scalability, performance, and upgrades.\",\n      \"des2\": \"From WordPress CMS development services for small businesses to enterprise platforms like Sitecore and Umbraco CMS development, we ensure your solution grows with you. Our CMS developers also integrate SEO, analytics, and marketing tools, so you always have the insights needed to attract and convert customers. Our clients trust us to provide powerful custom CMS development services that improve efficiency and customer engagement. Whether you need Drupal CMS development, Sitecore CMS development, or a complete custom CMS website development, we ensure your platform is secure, scalable, and user-friendly.\"\n    },\n    \"section7\": {\n      \"quote\": \"Allspark transformed the way we manage our website. Their team built a custom CMS tailored to our needs, making updates seamless and boosting our online presence.\",\n      \"author\": \"Michael Harris, Marketing Director\"\n    },\n    \"section8\": {\n      \"image\": \"img3.png\",\n      \"title\": \"Why Choose Allspark Technologies for CMS Development\",\n      \"data\": [\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Flexible CMS Options\",\n          \"description\": \"From WordPress to Sitecore, our CMS developers help you choose the right system for your business.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Secure & Scalable Solutions\",\n          \"description\": \"We design CMS platforms that grow with your company and protect sensitive data.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"User-Friendly Management\",\n          \"description\": \"Our CMS web development services prioritize simple dashboards for easy updates.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"title\": \"Dedicated CMS Developers\",\n          \"description\": \"Whether you need a freelance CMS developer alternative or a full team, we offer dedicated CMS developers for every project.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"section9\": {\n      \"title\": \"Industries We Serve\",\n      \"para\": \"We provide CMS solutions across industries such as:\",\n      \"industries\": [\n        \"E-commerce & Retail\",\n        \"Healthcare & Pharma\",\n        \"Education & E-learning\",\n        \"Finance & Banking\",\n        \"Media & Entertainment\",\n        \"B2B Enterprises\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"faq\": {\n      \"title\": \"FAQs – Answering Your Concerns\",\n      \"faqs\": [\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-1\",\n          \"ques\": \"What is CMS in web development?\",\n          \"ans\": \"CMS (Content Management System) is software that helps you create, edit, and manage website content without needing deep coding skills.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-2\",\n          \"ques\": \"Which is the best CMS for developers?\",\n          \"ans\": \"It depends on your needs, WordPress for speed, Drupal for flexibility, Sitecore for enterprise, or Craft CMS for design-driven projects.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-3\",\n          \"ques\": \"Can you migrate my site to a new CMS?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Yes, our CMS website development company provides migration services to ensure a smooth, secure transition.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"item\": \"item-4\",\n          \"ques\": \"Do you offer support after launch?\",\n          \"ans\": \"Absolutely. Our CMS development services include long-term support, updates, and training.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n}');
